Package: bayr
Type: Package
Title: dplyr/tidyr based manipulation of MCMC chains
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-02-04
Author: Martin Schmettow
Maintainer: Martin Schmettow <schmettow@web.de>
Description: This package aims at being a tool set for reporting
		of Bayesian (generalized linear mixed-effect) regression models.
		A set of wrapper functions unifies extraction of MCMC chains
		from varios Bayesian implementations. Posterior distributions
		are stored in	a common annotarted long format to facilitate further
    processing with dplyr/tidyr and ggplot2.
LazyData: TRUE
License: GPL-3
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    testthat,
    MCMCglmm,
		brms
Depends:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    modeest
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
